  "detailed_description": "<h1>My Other Games</h1><p><br><br><br><br></p><br><h1>About the Game</h1>Forget about running and jumping. In Explosive Candy World you have to EXPLODE your way to the end of the level!<br><br>It's a physics-based platformer game with a fun and weird movement mechanic.<br><br>Use your mouse or analog stick to adjust the strength, then release to throw a mighty explosive candy! Throw it at buttons, switches, breakable stuff, or even at yourself!<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1469960/extras/b5a8801847c058919cafe6c5863a1a5e.poster.avif?t=1725041048\" width=480 height=270 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1469960/extras/b5a8801847c058919cafe6c5863a1a5e.webm?t=1725041048\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1469960/extras/b5a8801847c058919cafe6c5863a1a5e.mp4?t=1725041048\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1469960/extras/755bcc81732caaa7404d19f0f3af4512.poster.avif?t=1725041048\" width=480 height=270 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1469960/extras/755bcc81732caaa7404d19f0f3af4512.webm?t=1725041048\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1469960/extras/755bcc81732caaa7404d19f0f3af4512.mp4?t=1725041048\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><strong>Features</strong><br><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li> Over 80 explosive levels scattered across 4 candy worlds (+ 1 secret world)<br></li><li> Cute, colorful pixel art<br></li><li> Original retro soundtrack<br></li><li> An unusual platformer, for fans of the genre who are tired of samey gameplay<br></li><li> The game has absolutely zero text, except for names and numbers. It's non-stop gameplay, with no reading!</li></ul><br>Some levels can be quite tricky, but keep trying! You respawn very fast and the levels are short and sweet<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1469960/extras/104fb0138bc22888ef4a6b928003813b.poster.avif?t=1725041048\" width=480 height=270 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1469960/extras/104fb0138bc22888ef4a6b928003813b.webm?t=1725041048\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1469960/extras/104fb0138bc22888ef4a6b928003813b.mp4?t=1725041048\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>",
  "about_the_game": "Forget about running and jumping. In Explosive Candy World you have to EXPLODE your way to the end of the level!<br><br>It's a physics-based platformer game with a fun and weird movement mechanic.<br><br>Use your mouse or analog stick to adjust the strength, then release to throw a mighty explosive candy! Throw it at buttons, switches, breakable stuff, or even at yourself!<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1469960/extras/b5a8801847c058919cafe6c5863a1a5e.poster.avif?t=1725041048\" width=480 height=270 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1469960/extras/b5a8801847c058919cafe6c5863a1a5e.webm?t=1725041048\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1469960/extras/b5a8801847c058919cafe6c5863a1a5e.mp4?t=1725041048\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1469960/extras/755bcc81732caaa7404d19f0f3af4512.poster.avif?t=1725041048\" width=480 height=270 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1469960/extras/755bcc81732caaa7404d19f0f3af4512.webm?t=1725041048\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1469960/extras/755bcc81732caaa7404d19f0f3af4512.mp4?t=1725041048\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><strong>Features</strong><br><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li> Over 80 explosive levels scattered across 4 candy worlds (+ 1 secret world)<br></li><li> Cute, colorful pixel art<br></li><li> Original retro soundtrack<br></li><li> An unusual platformer, for fans of the genre who are tired of samey gameplay<br></li><li> The game has absolutely zero text, except for names and numbers. It's non-stop gameplay, with no reading!</li></ul><br>Some levels can be quite tricky, but keep trying! You respawn very fast and the levels are short and sweet<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1469960/extras/104fb0138bc22888ef4a6b928003813b.poster.avif?t=1725041048\" width=480 height=270 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1469960/extras/104fb0138bc22888ef4a6b928003813b.webm?t=1725041048\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1469960/extras/104fb0138bc22888ef4a6b928003813b.mp4?t=1725041048\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>",
